      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.size
      value: 17
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[0].line
      value: The sky used to be a promise.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[1].line
      value: 'Amber used to be blue. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[2].line
      value: The world was replenished.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[3].line
      value: There is a particular sound water makes when it is unafraid.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[4].line
      value: We took it for granted.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[5].line
      value: The way you take for granted a word you use every day.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[6].line
      value: Until the morning it means something else.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[7].line
      value: 'The heat blew like a storm. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[8].line
      value: It rose and sank the rivers.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[9].line
      value: The world closed its eyes.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[10].line
      value: And by evening it was over.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[11].line
      value: It was all a blur.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[12].line
      value: 'The world awaited its sleep. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[13].line
      value: But it never happened.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2483668177161727343, guid: e3ce64cb87e80aa4b8197122a403999c, type: 3}
      propertyPath: storyLines.Array.data[14].line
      value: Because one small thing . . .
